{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Beginner Spoiler}}
'''''Muflliato''''' is a spell that "fills the ears with an unidentifiable buzzing sound."
== Analysis ==
Muffliato was one of the spells Harry found in the Half Blood Prince's copy of the ''Advanced Potion Making'' textbook.
